		In order to cover our monthly server/bandwidth charges, along with countless uncompensated hours working to provide our services to you, we have decided to charge a one-time fee of $2.97 per profile for use of our 'Autosync' feature. This fee is a one-time fee and you will never be required to pay again.<br>
